        <h3 class="title">Personal information is sold</h3>

        
        <p class="para pt-3 pb-3" style="text-align: justify;">Your personal information is never traded, rented, or loaned to other parties. However, we may engage in activities that, depending on your privacy preferences, could be construed as a "sale" under certain laws, such as providing social media platforms, analytics providers, and advertising firms with your information from the Identifiers and Internet or network activity data sections of the above chart. For further details on your privacy choices, see the Manage Your Information part of this Policy.
