        <h3 class="title">Personal information preservation</h3>

        
        <p class="para pt-3 pb-3" style="text-align: justify;">We keep your personal information for as long as it is reasonably necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was obtained, to comply with legal requirements, to settle disputes, to prevent fraud, and to enforce our agreements. Your Personal Information's amount, nature, and sensitivity are taken into account, as well as the risk of harm from unauthorised use or disclosure, the purposes for which it is processed, whether those purposes can be achieved through other means, and any applicable legal requirements.
